                        <p class="text-gray-400">Most importantly, we have successfully integrated our company with the world's leading financial platforms! We are connected with Stripe, our main payment processor, and have secured banking partners – Thread Bank, Relay Financial, and Wise Bank. This allows us to receive and send payments securely, quickly, and in compliance with all international standards, in multiple currencies.</p>
