            <p class="mt-6">By purchasing an SFLicense, you secure your position and ownership in the SFT21 ecosystem at the very beginning of its creation, and an opportunity for passive bonuses (which will not be possible later under the same conditions). After that, you have complete freedom to decide whether and when to activate the Franchise and start actively building your business. Precisely that flexibility makes the SFT21 model unique.</p>
            
